works.description:
The copyrighted work at issue are various
 
recipes and recipe cards that appear on wonderfullifee.com.

Also, please note that I had filed a previous complaint about this same  
blog and Google had removed the images. The user seems to have reposted  
them with my credit removed. I have a copy of the email that was sent to
me  
stating that the same content had been removed before. Please let me know 

if you would like to see the email.
